<section class="gov-section sm">
  <div class="gov-container col center gap-48">
    <div class="gov-title-wrap center">
      <div class="gov-eyebrow muted">[How SPECTRE fits]</div>
      <h2 class="max-w-586">
        Policy logic between the device and the secure path
      </h2>
    </div>
    <p class="gov-description max-w-780">
      SPECTRE governs path selection, switching logic, and profile behavior. It
      uses policy inputs such as availability, signal, location, mission rules,
      and operating conditions to determine the best path for the device.
      EdgeConnect then delivers that selected path through controlled
      infrastructure.
    </p>
    <div class="gov-image-wrapper">
      <img src="/assets/sp-fits.png" alt="SPECTRE Fits" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
